    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >How to God is an immersive VR god simulation game allowing you to step into the divine sandals of a beginner god. Build villages, raise a unique creature, follow branching quests, battle rival deities, and command the elements to unlock new powers.   </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>😈 Choose your creature</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Spawn a mighty creature to do your bidding! Train it with rewards or punishment, then watch it grow into a fierce and powerful force.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3270840/extras/060f05de3b65c9a7b2a06f00cc81c3f7.poster.avif?t=1772192929\" width=1170 height=390 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3270840/extras/060f05de3b65c9a7b2a06f00cc81c3f7.webm?t=1772192929\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3270840/extras/060f05de3b65c9a7b2a06f00cc81c3f7.mp4?t=1772192929\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>⚔️ Battle against rival gods</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Other divine beings will challenge your authority. Hone your combat skills and solve tricky puzzles to fight off these almighty foes.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3270840/extras/e5d508160c08ffc96553ee1871563f4b.poster.avif?t=1772192929\" width=1170 height=390 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3270840/extras/e5d508160c08ffc96553ee1871563f4b.webm?t=1772192929\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3270840/extras/e5d508160c08ffc96553ee1871563f4b.mp4?t=1772192929\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🔮 <strong>Harness Alchemy</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Combine materials to create something new - try it with villagers, too!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3270840/extras/b6236f734cd1d0ff2b7447a06411fc1f.poster.avif?t=1772192929\" width=1170 height=390 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3270840/extras/b6236f734cd1d0ff2b7447a06411fc1f.webm?t=1772192929\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3270840/extras/b6236f734cd1d0ff2b7447a06411fc1f.mp4?t=1772192929\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>🛖 Shape civilizations</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Construct everything from humble homes to sacred shrines and more.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3270840/extras/587b88c1aa2fdff111e084a578f5cbbb.poster.avif?t=1772192929\" width=1170 height=390 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3270840/extras/587b88c1aa2fdff111e084a578f5cbbb.webm?t=1772192929\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3270840/extras/587b88c1aa2fdff111e084a578f5cbbb.mp4?t=1772192929\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>🔨 Upgrade your godly abilities</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Choose from many arcane powers and unleash your own unique brand of godly might!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3270840/extras/6bb1b2b362a64c4b5655fc8e5060f6ed.poster.avif?t=1772192929\" width=1170 height=390 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3270840/extras/6bb1b2b362a64c4b5655fc8e5060f6ed.webm?t=1772192929\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3270840/extras/6bb1b2b362a64c4b5655fc8e5060f6ed.mp4?t=1772192929\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Wield your godly might, shape the world with your choices, and learn How to God.</p>",
